      "content": "hey so im living in oslo and the winter is killing me lol. i feel so drained all the time and i want to really kickstart my immune system. i read online that taking like 50,000 IU of vitamin d every day for a few weeks can basically reset your levels and stop you from getting sick. is that safe to do if i just do it for a short burst?",
