      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get the caution but 600 iu feels like nothing when it's pitch black all day here. i've seen a lot of wellness influencers and biohacking forums saying that high-dose loading phases are actually the most efficient way to fix a deficiency quickly. if i only do it for like 10-14 days, wouldn't the body just process it? it seems like a small risk to take to actually feel human again.",
